# <p><strong>Description</strong></p>
# <p>This Custom Transformer read the content of a Socrata server.  All the information is read and all the information is transformed into FME attributes.</p>
# <p><strong>Input Ports</strong></p>
# <ul>
# <li>Input: One feature needed to start the reading of the Socrata server.</li>
# </ul>
# <p><strong>Output Ports</strong></p>
# <ul>
# <li>Output: One feature for each metadata record read from the Socrata server.</li>
# </ul>
# <p><strong>Parameters</strong></p>
# <ul>
# <li>Domain: The url of the Socrata server.</li>
# </ul>
